---
title: Spicy Chicken Coconut Curry Soup with Chickpeas, Cauliflower & Toast
description: Northern Indian flavors take center stage in this lush, savory-sweet, and spicy soup. Here, aromatic onion, garam masala, curry, and tomato paste are cooked just until fragrant. Next, cauliflower and chickpeas are added to create another layer of dimension—all simmered in coconut milk and savory vegetable stock, and all in one pot! Scallion greens are sprinkled over top for a pop of freshness. Toasted ciabatta adds a crisp crunch on the side.
